    {
      "id": "95",
      "name": "Medya",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/11/30/35428890/5436bc37c9fa8bbe7f08a76db7291394_2765378202140216845.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "December 26, 2021",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Where light can barely reach, a treacherous foe lies in wait in the shadows.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "In a realm void of sunlight, the remaining kindlings still burn.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "And where the sun shines, people's hopes spring eternal.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "These heartfelt wishes sparkle as bright as fireworks blooming in the sky.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/10/237301566/03c205a44b83d0e7542ddcdd33101468_8561098290191154309.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "February 4, 2022",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "The ancient Sacred Sakura stands on the peak of Mt. Yougou, its roots running long and deep into the earth, stretching endlessly.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Underneath its shadow, there are people who wholeheartedly wish for blessings, a kitsune who is amused at the floating world, and a god who yearns for transient eternity.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Everything in this world changes, people come and go, but the Sacred Sakura blooms brilliantly every year, its petals going where the wind leads.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
